var geoCoordMap = {
  'Russia': [100, 60],
  'United States': [-99, 38],
  'United States of America': [-99, 38]
};
export default function fixGeoCoords(mapType, region) {
  if (mapType === 'world') {
    var geoCoord = geoCoordMap[region.name];

    if (geoCoord) {
      var cp = [geoCoord[0], geoCoord[1]];
      region.setCenter(cp);
    }
  }
}
